query:
/*+  */ select count(*)
from question AS q
inner join tag_question AS tq
on tq.question_id = q.id AND q.view_count >= 100 AND q.view_count <= 100000
inner join site AS s
on tq.site_id = s.site_id AND q.site_id = s.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('stackoverflow')
inner join tag AS t
on tq.tag_id = t.id AND t.site_id = s.site_id AND t.name IN ('ado',
'angular-routing',
'babel',
'boto3',
'delphi-xe5',
'dispatcher',
'file-handling',
'flash-builder',
'nsfilemanager',
'traits',
'wampserver');
